51
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:10,800
[UNKNOWN] Oca.

52
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] Što je svjedočanstvo Kristovo?

53
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,480
