68
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:47,040
[SPEAKER_00] Mi mijenjamo, istina se kroji po nama.

69
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,319
[SPEAKER_00] Krist je jedina istina.

70
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa ako istinu svedemo na ovu razinu, na našu razinu?

71
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:56,720
