75
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:09,920
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je istina za Njemce u tom trenutku ako ubije Židova?

76
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:15,040
[SPEAKER_01] Da nije ubio čovjeka, zar ne?

77
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,680
[UNKNOWN] To je istina.

78
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:26,480
